thread.title: Keith Richardson

author: Keith Richardson
title: Keith Richardson
text:
My wife was at the house when they installed it. She spent the next 3 days telling me how wonderful the company and the installers were.
The net looks awesome. We got black. Highly recommend that color.
At the end of the day this company is full of good people which is why they are so good. Good people are hard to find. Thanks for the awesome net, great service and employing people that I'm proud to have in my house.
